.TH man 3 "11 November 2023" "1.0" "rlibstdio man page (reddlibc)"
.SH NAME
rlibstdio, clearstdin
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B #include <rlibstdio.h>

.B void clearstdin(void);
.SH DESCRIPTION
The
.B clearstdin()
.R function clears stdin.

.SH NOTES
When including this header, make sure to link reddlibc.a (in /usr/lib/ on default reddlibc installs) when compiling.
.SH SEE ALSO
rlibstr(3), rlibinput(3), rlibchar(3), rlibint(3)
.SH BUGS
No known bugs. Although some consider that they are a feature in C.
